            </div>
            <div class="uc-card__tags">
              <span class="uc-card__tag" style="--tag-color: #8b5cf6">Data 360</span>
              <span class="uc-card__tag" style="--tag-color: #22c55e">Agentforce</span>
            </div>
            <p class="uc-card__brief">Equip boutique advisors with an AI-powered companion that surfaces collector preferences, purchase history, and next-best-action recommendations during appointments</p>
            <div class="uc-card__details">
              <div class="uc-card__benefits">
                <h4>Key Benefits</h4>
                <ul>
                  <li>Instant access to unified collector profile during walk-ins or appointments</li>
                  <li>Agentforce-powered recommendations based on collection affinity and occasion</li>
                  <li>Previous interaction history across all boutiques globally</li>
                  <li>Higher conversion rates through informed, personalised consultations</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <p class="uc-card__related">Related: UC1 (Unified Profile), UC7 (Appointment Intelligence), UC2 (Collection Affinity)</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- UC7 -->
          <div class="uc-card" data-cluster="2" data-technologies="Data 360,Marketing Cloud" data-uc="7">
            <div class="uc-card__header">
              <span class="uc-card__badge" style="--cluster-color: #0D9488">UC7</span>
              <h3 class="uc-card__title">Appointment &amp; Walk-In Intelligence</h3>
              <button class="uc-card__expand" aria-label="Expand details"><i class="ph ph-caret-down"></i></button>
            </div>
            <div class="uc-card__tags">
              <span class="uc-card__tag" style="--tag-color: #8b5cf6">Data 360</span>
              <span class="uc-card__tag" style="--tag-color: #0176D3">Marketing Cloud</span>
            </div>
            <p class="uc-card__brief">Enrich appointment bookings with collector data and trigger pre-visit preparation flows for advisors, plus post-visit follow-up journeys</p>
            <div class="uc-card__details">
              <div class="uc-card__benefits">
                <h4>Key Benefits</h4>
                <ul>
                  <li>Pre-appointment briefing delivered to advisor with collector preferences</li>
                  <li>Automated post-visit thank-you and product information delivery</li>
                  <li>Walk-in traffic insights correlated with digital engagement data</li>
                  <li>Seamless handoff between online research and boutique experience</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <p class="uc-card__related">Related: UC6 (Clienteling), UC17 (Journey Orchestration)</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- UC8 -->
          <div class="uc-card" data-cluster="2" data-technologies="Data 360,Personalization" data-uc="8">
            <div class="uc-card__header">
              <span class="uc-card__badge" style="--cluster-color: #0D9488">UC8</span>
              <h3 class="uc-card__title">In-Boutique Digital Personalisation</h3>
              <button class="uc-card__expand" aria-label="Expand details"><i class="ph ph-caret-down"></i></button>
            </div>
            <div class="uc-card__tags">
              <span class="uc-card__tag" style="--tag-color: #8b5cf6">Data 360</span>
              <span class="uc-card__tag" style="--tag-color: #14b8a6">Personalization</span>
