              <div class="uc-card__benefits">
                <h4>Key Benefits</h4>
                <ul>
                  <li>Dynamic content on boutique screens tailored to visitor&rsquo;s collection interests</li>
                  <li>Try-on recommendations based on wrist size, past purchases, and preferences</li>
                  <li>Elevated brand experience bridging digital sophistication with physical luxury</li>
                  <li>Data captured from in-store interactions feeds back into the unified profile</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <p class="uc-card__related">Related: UC6 (Clienteling), UC14 (Product Recommendations)</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- UC9 -->
          <div class="uc-card" data-cluster="2" data-technologies="Data 360,Einstein AI" data-uc="9">
            <div class="uc-card__header">
              <span class="uc-card__badge" style="--cluster-color: #0D9488">UC9</span>
              <h3 class="uc-card__title">Event &amp; Exhibition Engagement Tracking</h3>
              <button class="uc-card__expand" aria-label="Expand details"><i class="ph ph-caret-down"></i></button>
            </div>
            <div class="uc-card__tags">
              <span class="uc-card__tag" style="--tag-color: #8b5cf6">Data 360</span>
              <span class="uc-card__tag" style="--tag-color: #f59e0b">Einstein AI</span>
            </div>
            <p class="uc-card__brief">Track collector engagement at Watches &amp; Wonders, SIHH, brand dinners, and local events to build rich behavioural profiles</p>
            <div class="uc-card__details">
              <div class="uc-card__benefits">
                <h4>Key Benefits</h4>
                <ul>
                  <li>Event attendance data integrated into unified collector profile</li>
                  <li>Post-event follow-up journeys triggered by specific interactions</li>
                  <li>RSVP and attendance patterns informing future event invitation targeting</li>
                  <li>Measure ROI of exclusive events through downstream purchase attribution</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <p class="uc-card__related">Related: UC20 (VIP Engagement), UC17 (Journey Orchestration)</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- UC10 -->
          <div class="uc-card" data-cluster="2" data-technologies="Data 360,Agentforce" data-uc="10">
            <div class="uc-card__header">
              <span class="uc-card__badge" style="--cluster-color: #0D9488">UC10</span>
              <h3 class="uc-card__title">Boutique Performance Analytics</h3>
              <button class="uc-card__expand" aria-label="Expand details"><i class="ph ph-caret-down"></i></button>
            </div>
            <div class="uc-card__tags">
              <span class="uc-card__tag" style="--tag-color: #8b5cf6">Data 360</span>
              <span class="uc-card__tag" style="--tag-color: #22c55e">Agentforce</span>
